      "acceptanceCriteria": "Nonlinear solver residuals converge to < 1e-5 for all load steps. Contact stabilization energy < 1% of total strain energy.",
      "rationale": "Force and displacement residuals converged to < 1e-6 for all 200 load increments. Contact stabilization energy monitored across all load steps and remained below 0.3% of total strain energy. Gradation 2 requirements satisfied."
