      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent peer review of model setup, boundary conditions, and material assignments conducted by a second analyst not involved in original model development.",
      "rationale": "A second qualified FEA analyst independently reviewed all model inputs, boundary conditions, contact definitions, and material properties against the documented modeling protocol. No errors or deviations identified. Gradation 2 achieved."
