      "rationale": "Elastic modulus and yield strength for Ti-6Al-4V sourced from tensile coupon tests on material from the same lot as the test constructs (n=5 coupons; E = 114.2 ± 1.8 GPa, Sy = 897 ± 12 MPa). UHMWPE block stiffness from compression testing per ASTM D695. All nominal dimensions verified by CMM to within ±0.02 mm. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
