      "rationale": "Each of the 11 FEA model instances was parameterized using as-measured CMM dimensions and lot-matched material property data from the corresponding physical construct. Boundary conditions replicate the F1717 fixture constraints as documented in the test protocol. Full traceability table linking model inputs to physical measurements provided in the analysis report. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
