      "rationale": "For all three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) across all 11 constructs: maximum percent difference = 6.8%; maximum E/uval = 1.42. Both acceptance criteria satisfied for every construct-QoI combination. Experimental uncertainty estimated from repeat measurements and inter-laboratory variability. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
