      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three primary QoIs specified in ASTM F1717 and constitute the basis for the regulatory performance claim. These QoIs directly characterize the mechanical behavior relevant to in vivo loading of the pedicle screw construct. Gradation 3 justified."
