      "rationale": "The validation activity uses the identical FEA model, material definitions, and boundary conditions as those employed for the regulatory submission prediction. The F1717 compression-bending test directly replicates the loading mode of interest. The non-cannulated 7.5 mm geometry validated here is the exact geometry of the submission device. Gradation 3 achieved."
